data.name: bunifuLabel1.Text
data.value: The Book Hub System is Software that Is Designed to Manage All the Functions of a Library. It Helps Librarian to Maintain the Database of New Books and the Books that are Borrowed by Members Along with their Due Dates. This System Completely Automates All Your Library's Activities.
